author: Google
description:
Broadcasting live, we are showcasing the latest "Nano Banana Pro" capabilities in AI Studio, demonstrating how users can master next-gen image generation and editing. Hosts Logan Kilpatrick, Ammaar Reshi, Kat Kampf, Naina Raisinghani, and Bea Alessio will "vibe code" apps live to highlight breakthrough features like SOTA text rendering, multi-image editing for character consistency, and search tool calling. The team will build diverse demos in real-time—ranging from 4K wallpaper apps and interactive newspapers featuring Veo video integration to cultural translation tools and full marketing campaigns. 

#NanoBanana #GoogleGemini #gemini3 

00:00 - Intro: Nano Banana Pro Launch
03:15 - Demo: Vibe Coding a Comic Book (Start)
07:30 - Nano Banana Pro Overview: Logic & Inputs
11:45 - Demo: Professional Brand Design (Toothpaste Pitch)
16:20 - Comic Book Results & Branching Storylines
21:10 - Search Grounding: Video Game Character Stats
25:40 - Demo: Turning Video into Visual Explainers
30:15
title: Nano Banana Pro | Live from Mountain View
